# Lottie Animation Files

Place your Lottie JSON animation files here.

## Recommended animations:

1. Download from https://lottiefiles.com/
2. Name files to match GiftType:
   - rose.json
   - chocolate.json
   - bear.json
   - diamond.json
   - crown.json
   - castle.json

3. Update GiftAnimation.tsx to import them:
   ```js
   const ANIMATION_SOURCES = {
     rose: require('./assets/animations/rose.json'),
     // ...
   };
   ```

